___status.description: Current status of the job execution

___subordinationType.description: Type of subordination to another JobExecution entities

___errorStatus.description: Status that describe error state of job execution

___completedDate.description: Date and time when the job execution completed

___uiStatus.description: Status that is rendered on UI

___startedDate.description: Date and time when the job execution started

___userId.description: ID of the user who created the JobExecution

___total.description: Total number of records to be processed

___runBy.description: First and last name of the user that triggered the job execution

___parentJobId.description: Id of the parent JobExecution entity

___parentJobExecutionId.description: UUID of the JobExecution entity which is parent for all JobExecution entities in a scope of one file upload process
